          },
          "reviewBody": "Okay. Writing this  after reading a couple of reviews. I could see some positive comments from few. I have also heard from the same ppl complaining about the school. Anyway.  If u really want ur kid or kids to prosper this isn't the right place at all. This school gives only education.  No manners, values or discipline has been taught. The center head is such a disrespectful person towards parents and few teachers are incapable of handling situations. No respect for parents too. ITS A ZERO QUALITY SCHOOL IN TOTAL.  I'd say this is the alert ⚠️ msg for the new parents and upcoming parents.",
